titlealts.searchtitle: Data Element: NEWBORN BLOOD SPOT TEST OUTCOME STATUS CODE (MAPLE SYRUP URINE DISEASE) - Description

body.p: NEWBORN BLOOD SPOT TEST OUTCOME STATUS CODE (MAPLE SYRUP URINE DISEASE) is the same as attribute NEWBORN BLOOD SPOT TEST OUTCOME STATUS .
NEWBORN BLOOD SPOT TEST OUTCOME STATUS CODE (MAPLE SYRUP URINE DISEASE) is the result of screening for Maple Syrup Urine Disease (MSUD).
